name: Jenna Coleman
description:
Jenna-Louise Coleman (born 27 April 1986), known professionally as Jenna Coleman, is an English actress. She is known for her roles as Jasmine Thomas in the soap opera Emmerdale, Clara Oswald in the science-fiction series Doctor Who, Queen Victoria in the period drama Victoria, Joanna Lindsay in the crime miniseries The Cry, and Marie-Andrée Leclerc in the crime miniseries The Serpent.

If you like my work, a review is more than welcome! Also, follow me on Twitter or Instagram!

Looking for something... spicy? Here's my Patreon!

Also, I recently started a blog where I will gather resources and tutorials about my work here!

Hey nice people! To celebrate my 100 followers milestone, here's my textual inversion of Jenna Coleman! I used 30 public images of her with a 2000 steps process. To use it in your works:

  • download the file and place it into stable-diffusion-webui>embeddings folder;

  • add jencoleman86 to your prompt;

  • keep the sampling steps around 20/25, and CFG between 7 and 8 to work well. Great results with DPM++ SDE Karras & Edge of Realism;
